high_descs: Turn left and walk straight then turn right and face the TV stand
Pick up the watch from the TV stand
Turn around and walk straight then face the left coffee table in front of the sofa
Place the watch on the silver plate on the table
Pick up the silver plate with the watch on it
Turn to the left and walk straight towards the TV stand
Place the silver plate with watch on the TV stand
anns.task_desc: Pick up the watch and place it on the silver plate

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn right to face the television.
Pick up the watch that is on the wooden table in front of the television.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the wooden coffee table.
Put the watch on the white and black plate that is on the coffee table.
Pick up the white and black plate with the watch on it off of the coffee table.
Turn around and walk up to the couch, then turn right and walk over to the wooden table that the television is on.
Put the plate with the watch on it down on the wooden table in front of the television.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a watch on it on a wooden table.

high_descs: Move to stand facing the television.
Pick up the watch in front of the television on the table.
Carry the watch to stand between the sofa and coffee table, so you're facing the coffee table.
Place the watch on the tray on top of the coffee table.
Pick up the tray with the watch on top from the coffee table.
Turn and carry the tray with the watch back to the table with the TV on top.
Place the tray with the watch on the table in front of the television.
anns.task_desc: Place a tray beneath a watch on the table.
